FBIS4-20099 "drweu080_i_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-080 Daily Report 26 Apr 1994 FRANCE Juppe: Helicopter Crews To Ignore Serb Controls Juppe: Helicopter Crews To Ignore Serb Controls LD2604085094 Paris Radio France International in French 0800 GMT 26 Apr 94 LD2604085094 Paris Radio France International French BFN [Text] France says the controls imposed by the Serbs on the evacuation by helicopter of wounded people from Gorazde are unacceptable. Paris ordered the crews of French helicopters involved in these missions to refuse to submit to these controls. This was stressed by the French Foreign Ministry yesterday evening. These Serb controls are reported to have quadrupled travelling times for the evacuations.
